name: H=N till I die
description: H=N till I die by Jarrett Cross | 2021 | Digital Art | Cheers to 100 days of H=N! In this 100 days, the H=N Community has inspired me immensely. It has inspired me to become a better artist. And not just that. It also has motivated me to push my limits to become a better person in my everyday life. I thank each and everyone of you. H=N till we die.
